OL,3,CMan arrested after 35-year-old woman
OL,4,Cfound dead in Hawick
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a 35-year-old
OL,8,Fwoman in Hawick.
OL,10,FPolice Scotland were called to a
OL,11,Fproperty in the Scottish Borders town
OL,12,Fat around 7:20am on Thursday.
OL,14,FIn a a statement Police Scotland said:
OL,15,F"Around 7.20am on Thursday, 25 June,
OL,16,F2026, we were called to the death of a
OL,17,F35-year-old woman at a property on
OL,18,FMcLagan Drive in Hawick. Next of kin
OL,19,Fis aware.
