OL,3,CMan arrested after 35-year-old woman
OL,4,Cfound dead in Hawick
OL,6,F"The death is being treated as
OL,7,Fsuspicious and enquiries are ongoing.
OL,9,F"A 39-year-old man has been arrested
OL,10,Fin connection with assault and
OL,11,Fenquiries are ongoing."
